question_string: What data format does CHEMDNER corpus have?
Where did the study with maximal geographic scale take place?
generated_sparql:
SELECT ?location
WHERE {
    ?study a orkgc:C20094 .
    ?study orkgp:P30013 ?scale .
    ?study orkgp:P30012 ?location .
}
ORDER BY DESC(?scale)
LIMIT 1

question_string: What quantity of iron oxide was discovered on Elorza crater?
gold_sparql:
SELECT ?properties_values, ?property_description
WHERE {
  ?papers rdf:type orkgc:Paper.
  ?papers rdfs:label ?papers_labels.
  FILTER(REGEX(?papers_labels, "Elorza crater", "i"))
  ?papers orkgp:P31 ?contrib.
  ?contrib ?properties ?properties_values.
  ?properties rdfs:label ?properties_labels.
  FILTER(REGEX(?properties_labels, "FeO"))
  ?properties orkgp:description ?property_description.
}
generated_sparql:
SELECT ?quantity WHERE {
    ?statement rdf:subject ?location .
    ?location rdfs:label "Elorza crater" .
    ?statement rdf:object ?object .
    ?object orkgp:P7000 <http://orkg.org/orkg/resource/wikidata:Q721849> .
    ?object orkgp:P1101 ?quantity .
}

question_string: What types of nanocarriers do have therapeutic effect?
gold_sparql:
SELECT ?types_of_nanocarriers, ?types_of_nanocarriers_labels
WHERE {
  orkgr:R144364 orkgp:compareContribution ?contrib.
  ?contrib orkgp:P41740 ?types_of_nanocarriers.
  ?contrib orkgp:P41743 ?therapeutic_effect.
  FILTER(?therapeutic_effect = "T"^^xsd:string)
  ?types_of_nanocarriers rdfs:label ?types_of_nanocarriers_labels.
}
generated_sparql:
SELECT DISTINCT ?nanocarrier ?nanocarrier_label
WHERE {
    ?comparison orkgp:P40 orkgr:R144265 .
    ?comparison orkgp:P32 ?contribution .
    ?contribution orkgp:P31 ?nanocarrier .
    ?nanocarrier a orkgc:C20042 .
    ?nanocarrier rdfs:label ?nanocarrier_label .
}

question_string: What models are being evaluated on the TDMSci dataset?
generated_sparql:
SELECT DISTINCT ?model_label
WHERE {
    ?dataset rdfs:label "TDMSci dataset" .
    ?contribution orkgp:P31 ?dataset .
    ?contribution orkgp:P23049 ?models_group .
    ?models_group rdfs:label "models" .
    ?models_group orkgp:P25041 ?model .
    ?model rdfs:label ?model_label .
}

question_string: List the title and ID of research papers that contain a benchmark over the Penn Treebank (Word Level) dataset?
generated_sparql:
SELECT DISTINCT ?paper ?title
WHERE {
    ?paper a orkgc:Paper .
    ?paper rdfs:label ?title .
    ?paper orkgp:P32 ?contribution .
    ?contribution a orkgc:Comparison .
    ?contribution orkgp:P27 ?dataset .
    ?dataset rdfs:label "Penn Treebank (Word Level)" .
}

question_string: Provide a list of papers that have utilized the Flair-TDM model and include the links to their code?
Where can I find code references in papers that have used the CATTS-XSUM model for benchmarking purposes?
generated_sparql:
SELECT ?paper ?codeReference
WHERE {
  ?model rdfs:label "CATTS-XSUM"^^xsd:string .
  ?contribution orkgp:HAS_MODEL ?model .
  ?paper orkgp:P31 ?contribution .
  ?paper a orkgc:Paper .
  ?paper orkgp:P160002 ?codeReference .
}
